</head>
<body>
<div class="container info-page">
  <div class="row pt-4 pb-3">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="header mb-3">
          <a href="/" class="text-decoration-none">
            <img src="/images/info.png" class="img-fluid" alt="">
          </a>
        </div>
        <a class="info-link" href="/">home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-6 mr-lg-auto">
      <div class="project_content">
        <p>Former Executive Creative Director at BBDO New York. I oversaw Snickers and Mars petcare brands with my former partner Peter Kain. We created the “You’re not you when you’re hungry” campaign for Snickers. It began with the 2010 admeter-winning commercial starting Betty White, and has since gone on to win every major award from Cannes Lions to Effies, while helping Snickers grow from the #7 to #1 global chocolate bar. Most recently, we won the One Show Penta award, honoring long term client-agency relationships and we picked up our second Super Clio for 2020’s “Fix the World” Super Bowl campaign.</p>
        <p>I also worked on US and global advertising for Mars petcare brands, including Pedigree’s Dogs on Zoom campaign to facilitate dog adoption during quarantine. During our tenure at BBDO, Peter and I wrote and oversaw award winning work for FedEx, Mountain Dew, Twix, and others. </p>
        <p>Currently freelancing and enjoying more time with my family.</p>

        <h2 class="text-uppercase">Experience</h2>
        <p>BBDO NEW YORK (2004-2021)<br>
        Snickers, Twix, FedEx, Mountain Dew Brands, Sony, Guinness Brands, Pedigree, Nutro, Cesar<br>
        BARTLE BOGLE HEGARTY (1999-2004) Axe, Levi’s, Johnnie Walker, Lipton, Feeding Children Better<br>
        BERLIN CAMERON (1999) Reebok, Coca-Cola</p>
        <h2 class="text-uppercase">Education</h2>
        <p>
          Syracuse University, School of Visual and Performing Arts. BA, Advertising<br>
          Cooper Union School of Fine Arts
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-uppercase">Awards & Recognition</h2>
        <p>
          One Show Penta Award<br>
          2015 and 2020 Super Clio<br>
          3x Emmy nominees<br>
          Cannes Lions (Film, Press, Cyber, Effectiveness)<br>
          One Show<br>
          One Show Entertainment<br>
          D&AD<br>
          AICP<br>
          Effies<br>
          Art Directors Club<br>
          Andy Awards<br>
          Kelly Awards<br>
          Mercury Awards<br>
          Clio Awards<br>
          Communication Arts
          </p>
        <directlink id="dl_2860906" link="https://www.arenakain.com/Info"></directlink>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">

    {% for project in data %}
    <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 mb-4">
      <a href=".{{ project.url }}.html" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="{{ project.image }}" class="card-img-top" alt="{{ project.name }}">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-center m-0">{{ project.name }}</h5>
            <p class="card-text text-center">
              {% for tag in project.tags %}
                <a href="{{ tag }}.html">{{ tag }}</a>{{ ", " if not loop.last else "" }}
              {% endfor %}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
